---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - LogoPrompt.pro">
  <main class="legal-page">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Home</a>

    <h1>About Us</h1>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        At LogoPrompt.pro, we believe that great design should be accessible to everyone. Our mission is to
        democratize logo creation by providing high-quality AI prompts that inspire creativity and help
        bring your brand vision to life.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>
        We curate and create carefully crafted prompts designed specifically for AI image generators like
        Ideogram, Google Gemini, and other leading platforms. Each prompt is optimized to produce
        professional-quality logo concepts that you can use as inspiration or starting points for your brand.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Curated Prompts:</strong> Every prompt in our collection is tested and refined to
        ensure high-quality results across different AI platforms.</li>
        <li><strong>Diverse Styles:</strong> From minimalist designs to bold graphics, we cover a wide
        range of aesthetic styles to match any brand personality.</li>
        <li><strong>Easy to Use:</strong> Simply copy a prompt and paste it into your preferred AI
        image generator to start creating.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Why AI Logo Prompts?</h2>
      <p>
        AI-powered design tools have revolutionized the creative industry. With the right prompts,
        anyone can generate stunning logo concepts in seconds. We bridge the gap between complex AI
        technology and everyday users by providing ready-to-use prompts that deliver consistent,
        professional results.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Team</h2>
      <p>
        LogoPrompt.pro is built by a passionate team of designers, developers, and AI enthusiasts
        who understand both the creative process and the technical aspects of AI image generation.
        We're constantly exploring new techniques and updating our prompt library to stay at the
        forefront of AI-driven design.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        We love hearing from our community! Whether you have feedback, suggestions, or just want to
        say hello, feel free to <a href="/contact">reach out to us</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  p a {
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  p a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  ul {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  strong {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }
</style>
